================================================================================
THIRD-PARTY COMPONENTS
================================================================================

SeekerMail Desktop bundles third-party open-source components. As of the last
audit this comprises roughly 696 Rust crates (the desktop application) and 473
npm packages (the frontend), the overwhelming majority under permissive
licenses (MIT, Apache-2.0, BSD-2-Clause, BSD-3-Clause, ISC).

The complete, per-dependency license texts are generated into
THIRD-PARTY-NOTICES.md by `scripts/ci/generate-notice.sh` and ship with each
release build.

